      "text": "IAM Components",
      "action": "Key Concepts - IAM Components:",
      "url": null,
      "description": "• Users - Individual people or applications\n• Groups - Collections of users with similar permissions\n• Roles - Set of permissions that can be assumed\n• Policies - Documents that define permissions"
    },
    {
      "order": 5,
      "text": "Principle of Least Privilege",
      "action": "Principle of Least Privilege:",
      "url": null,
      "description": "Give users and services only the minimum permissions needed to do their job. This reduces the impact if credentials are compromised."
    },
    {
